International Call to Join the Revolution in Kurdistan
Jan 24, 2016
${data_prefix}pics/international-call-preview.jpg
Society, Video Reports
---
Across Bakûr (Turkish-occupied Kurdistan) youths have erected barricades and defend their neighborhoods against Turkish state forces. Internationalists in Rojava call to come to Kurdistan and take part in the revolutionary confederation.
